Sizmek Technologies, Inc.


                  Sizmek Technologies, Inc. provides digital advertising solutions. The firm's solutions are delivered through a scalable technology infrastructure that allows delivery of digital media advertising campaigns of any size. The company was founded by Gal Trifon, Ofer Zadikario, Amir Hardoof, Nir Ben Zvi and Guy Gamzu in September 1999 and is headquartered in New York, NY                





